–’Щ@60a939e5eaa39da689783a0f63fbf7e6b3f3650d3efbf1379c4cb983d6b6d776Щ~Title: title: polars group-by
Path: lazyframe
Content:









``polars group-by``
[link: /commands/categories/lazyframe.md] ’Щ@728220649d3b868b24dc935671a5d0e6c53c71bbd92853c764d9f29e61d4c170Щ]Title: title: polars group-by
Path: Signature
Content:
``> polars group-by {flags} ...rest``
’Щ@783d5042e3d18cb767bf6fd2fad2f8d2bdb268647f02a71dfcdcb79f382ef659ЩзTitle: title: polars group-by
Path: Flags
Content:
``--maintain-order, -m``
: Ensure that the order of the groups is consistent with the input data. This is slower than a default group by and cannot be run on the streaming engine.
’Щ@692b7eb94ed953f914fe00cf12eed35427aeadb3d11549e7d09fc2e47229b705ЩsTitle: title: polars group-by
Path: Parameters
Content:
``...rest``
: Expression(s) that define the lazy group-by.
’Щ@3e35eaf9048d6a65f7a852ce7dba7a9d76f6ec9ab752967e9c57494a2e46795bЩ’Title: title: polars group-by
Path: Input/output types:
Content:
input
output
polars_dataframe
polars_dataframe
polars_lazyframe
polars_lazyframe
’Щ@462ebd900c224caf270062c2e6826c32d883e9b1653a46a91a8ecd207722d941ЪTitle: title: polars group-by
Path: Examples
Content:
Group by and perform an aggregation
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [1 4] [2 6] [2 4]]
    | polars into-lazy
    | polars group-by a
    | polars agg [
        (polars col b | polars min | polars as "b_min")
        (polars col b | polars max | polars as "b_max")
        (polars col b | polars sum | polars as "b_sum")
     ]
    | polars collect
    | polars sort-by a
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ a в”Ӯ b_min в”Ӯ b_max в”Ӯ b_sum в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ     2 в”Ӯ     4 в”Ӯ     6 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ     4 в”Ӯ     6 в”Ӯ    10 в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Group by an expression and perform an aggregation
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [2025-04-01 1] [2025-04-02 2] [2025-04-03 3] [2025-04-04 4]]
    | polars into-lazy
    | polars group-by (polars col a | polars get-day | $in mod 2)
    | polars agg [
        (polars col b | polars min | polars as "b_min")
        (polars col b | polars max | polars as "b_max")
        (polars col b | polars sum | polars as "b_sum")
     ]
    | polars collect
    | polars sort-by a
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ a в”Ӯ b_min в”Ӯ b_max в”Ӯ b_sum в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ     2 в”Ӯ     4 в”Ӯ     6 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ     1 в”Ӯ     3 в”Ӯ     4 в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
